sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Sig as OS signal
    participant Main as main.go
    participant Store as BadgerDB
    participant Node as Node + HLC
    participant IBLT as IBLTState
    participant Gossip as Gossip
    participant Coord as Coordinator + Syncer
    participant Srv as gRPC server

    Note over Main: Boot

    Sig->>Main: start
    Main->>Store: open
    Store-->>Main: highest persisted HLC
    Main->>Node: create (HLC seeded above disk)
    Main->>IBLT: build from store
    Main->>Gossip: start + join seeds (blocks)
    Gossip-->>Main: ready
    Main->>Coord: wire coordinator + syncer
    Main->>Srv: register services + listen
    Main->>Coord: start anti-entropy loop
    Main->>Srv: serve

    Sig->>Main: SIGINT / SIGTERM
    Note over Main: Shutdown (reverse order)
    Main->>Srv: GracefulStop
    Main->>Coord: Close
    Main->>Gossip: Leave
    Main->>Store: Close
